    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/img/image_2021-01-09_16-24-45.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><h2 id="preface" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#preface" class="header-mark"></a>Preface</h2><p>Uh&hellip; there&rsquo;s really nothing much to say before this—a problem came up&hellip;</p>
<p>So I asked in the group, got it fixed, and now I&rsquo;m writing down how it was done&hellip;</p>
<p>I switched to i3wm, and when I tried to mount another partition using a file manager, this error popped up:</p>
<p><img class="tw:inline" loading="lazy" src='/img/image_2021-01-09_16-24-45.png'     ></p>
<p>This issue is usually caused by a missing package.</p>
<p>Well, basically I just forgot to install something.</p>
<p>What we need is <code>polkit</code>&hellip;</p>
<p>If you don&rsquo;t know what it is, check out this page on the Arch Wiki:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Polkit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Polkit - ArchWiki</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="the-solution-process" class="headerLink">
