<p>After installation, we also need to install its graphical frontend.</p>
<p>As shown, there are many to choose from:</p>
<p><img class="tw:inline" loading="lazy" src='/img/2021-01-16_23-40.png'     ></p>
<p>I&rsquo;ll go with Gnome&rsquo;s — it&rsquo;s what I&rsquo;m used to&hellip;</p>
