<p>But you&rsquo;d have to type that every time, and I think that&rsquo;s a hassle — rua～</p>
<p>So we need to set it to start on boot. Generally, you can do it like this:</p>
<p><img class="tw:inline" loading="lazy" src='/img/photo_2021-01-16_23-59-36.jpg'     ></p>
